div.p:
It may be within the rules of neutrality but I am afraid we could not convince the average citizen there was any difference in allowing a vessel to be completed here and allowing the parts to be made so that a complete vessel could be shipped and the parts assembled in another port.For correspondence previously printed concerning the sale of submarines in parts, see 
